Looking at the code, the issue is that `sendDataResult` is created but only partially initialized before being returned. In the early return case (when session is null or reqId is invalid), it returns completely uninitialized. In the normal return case, only `dataFlags`, `recvLargeDataFlags`, and `streamId` are set, leaving other fields uninitialized.

The fix is to initialize the `Connection` struct properly with default values.
